  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This investigation is designed to evaluate the at-home usability, performance, user
      acceptance and reliability of the Headgear with a CPAP Mask for a duration of 2-4 weeks.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Up to 300 participants will be recruited for the trial, consisting of male and female
      participants diagnosed with OSA and receiving CPAP or Bi-level PAP for the treatment of their
      OSA. These include current CPAP mask users.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
